<h2 id="modifier-keys">Modifier Keys</h2>

<h3 id="windows">Windows</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Internet Exlorer: Alt + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
  <li>Firefox: Alt + Shift + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
  <li>Google Chrome: Alt + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
  <li>Safari: Alt + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h3 id="linux">Linux</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Firefox: Alt + Shift + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
  <li>Google Chrome: Alt + Mod + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h3 id="os-x">OS X</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Firefox:  Ctrl + Opt + <access key="" number=""></access></li>
